	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65242905"><p>What Vance is saying here is that we cannot compete on merit in the same free market that Republicans are always telling us will solve all of our problems.</p><p>The other thing he's telling us is that the minimum wage is too low. "cheap labor is fundamentally a crutch" in a country where the minimum wage is not a living wage is a scum-sucking thing to say.</p><p>Of course, he didn't mean to tell us either of those things, but he's a spectacular idiot so he couldn't help it. What will he tell us next that we already know, that Trump is named more than anyone else in the Epstein files? That Trump is America's Hitler? No wait, he already told us that, before he decided to become America's Goering.</p></div>
	</div>

